{"tid":1238731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"FB反擊戰嘅手足入一入嚟唔該！","createTime":"2019-06-18T02:24:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T18:27:04.000Z","uid":16365,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e5bc1973b4cbfa46a26be89fac9349069121fd8d","tid":1238731,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:24:50.000Z","msg":"除咗分頭like 支持一哥同埋反一哥製造內鬥之外<br />\n仲有一啲方向畀大家做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 做番平時五毛分化民主派嘅嘢，屌9啲藍絲做鍵盤戰士無行動出嚟撐，尤其過埋何君堯個集會可以做呢樣嘢，屌9佢地道貌岸然，得把口，另一邊就話激進果邊言論偏激，拖梗政府後腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 鼓吹班廢中廢老政治冷感，因為你要佢藍轉黃幾乎係無可能，但你可以散播失敗主義，講撚到自己一路撐修例，但自己嘅支持被政府同建制派利用，話暫緩就暫緩，而家心灰意冷，以後都唔會再理政治，政治與我無關！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 連登仔最鍾意講嘅騎劫，唔使我eleborate啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">開工喇手足！！！！</span>"},{"pid":"997dd346770e805db9c0f186150dbf81a76f7037","tid":1238731,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:26:11.000Z","msg":"毒撚講嘢無人理"},{"pid":"e9a5655dcfe0e2bbc8c244d6c744f996a7c0076e","tid":1238731,"uid":145675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:32:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f61fa9761ff7492b7821244dc0d231f46a773ae7","tid":1238731,"uid":91604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:34:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4a0e15dda58e483f9e1acb3c3aed21bda4921f9","tid":1238731,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor